{"type":null,"faqId":12265,"title":"荣耀3C（H30-T00） 自动发送短信到第三方号码如何处理？","answer":"<span style=\"font-family:'simsun','serif';color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">荣耀</span><span style=\"font-family:'simsun','serif';color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">3C</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">的原生应用不会有通过后台发送短信的功能。可以先看下手机中都有哪些第三方应用有后台发送短信的功能并且是“允许”的权限，查看方法：手机管家</span><span style=\"font-family:'simsun','serif';color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">-&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">权限管理</span><span style=\"font-family:'simsun','serif';color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">-&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">安全防御</span><span style=\"font-family:'simsun','serif';color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">-&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">发送短信。在这里看看哪个应用的权限是“允许”。出厂时默认都是提示，如果用户设置为允许，就会出现第三方应用通过后台发送短信的功能，果断禁止就可以了。</span>","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3089","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1399257993000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":511,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}